      <tr>\r\n                                <td>dimensions</td>\r\n                                <td>\r\n                                    Returns the data for the individual dimensions passed in on the request. Also compares the scores of the returned dimensions and ranks the states accordingly.<p></p>\r\n                                    <p>Dimensions are passed in as a pipe-delimited list of the dimension name.</p>\r\n                                    <h4>Example</h4>\r\n                                    <p>http://life-measures.wdoitsolutions.com/api/index.php/us/scores/?key=yourRegistrationKey&amp;dimensions=opportunity|health_and_environment|freedom</p>\r\n                                    <div class="row">\r\n                                        <div class="large-12 medium-12 columns">\r\n                                            <div class="parameter-link">\r\n                                                <a href="#">Available U.S. &amp; World Dimensions\r\n                                                    <i class="fi-arrow-down"></i>\r\n                                                    <i class="fi-arrow-up"></i>\r\n                                                </a>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div class="parameter-list">\r\n                                                opportunity<br>\r\n                                                health_and_environment<br>\r\n                                                freedom<br>\r\n                                                community_and_relationships<br>\r\n                                                living_standard<br>\r\n                                                peace_and_security\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <p></p>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <p></p>\r\n    